title: Fantasy Extravaganza Finale (ft. Evan Silva)
itunes:title: Fantasy Extravaganza Finale (ft. Evan Silva)
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – react to the latest NFL news, including Cowboys quarterback Tony Romo leaving Thursday’s preseason game with a back injury, and the Browns trading Barkevious Mingo to the Patriots. Then the heroes invite Rotoworld Senior Editor Evan Silva to the show for an in-depth fantasy discussion to wrap up the 2016 ATN Fantasy Extravaganza. Plus, Martial Blitz returns with more pig skin & pop culture along with former NFL player Brian Westbrook.
